mips-lite.patch

From: Jason Wessel <jason.wessel@windriver.com>
Subject: [PATCH] This adds basic support to the MIPS architecture

This patch also adds support for the MIPS Malta (via 8250), SiByte
1250-SWARM (32 and 64bit, custom UART), all from Manish Lachwani, and
Toshiba TX493x platforms from Sergei Shtylyov.

